cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.PL, cs.MS, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper introduces a family of temporal logics to reason about systems with Zeno behaviors. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper discusses designing controllers to control such systems. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is another possible category as the paper extends linear-time temporal logic LTL. 
- cs.MS (Mathematical Software) is a possible category as the paper introduces a new class of succinct ordinal automata. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also a possible category as the paper discusses controlling systems with Zeno behaviors.
